Ancestral Katana		TYPE:Samurai		SOURCEPAGE:p.28	PREATT:4								DESC:Your katana has been handed down for generations, travelling through the hands of one samurai after another, all striving to honour the family name. Though you may not have known it at the time you began your career, taking this feat awakens the ancestors within the blade, allowing you to enhance the weapon as you gain experience.
Daisho Fighting		TYPE:Samurai		SOURCEPAGE:p.28	PREFEAT:2,Ambidexterity,Improved Two-Weapon Fighting	DESC:With a Katana in your right hand and a wakizashi in your other, you are able to attack more effectively or defend yourself more efficiently than if you were wielding but a single weapon.
Deadly Draw			TYPE:Samurai		SOURCEPAGE:p.29	PREATT:7	PREFEAT:1,Quick Draw	DESC:You have mastered the art of iaido and are able to execute a powerful slicing attack as you remove your katana from its scabbard.
Dead Shot			TYPE:Samurai		SOURCEPAGE:p.29	PREFEAT:1,Blind-Fight	PREATT:9	DESC:You are a master bowman and are able to pierce the concealment that protects your targets.
